{"tid":2496673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"何議員接受呢位年青人道歉, 令佢上咗人生寶貴嘅一課...","createTime":"2021-04-20T03:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T03:42:56.000Z","uid":175258,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aa6dc77bdb68e58af186cc31ecfa2b64c4cf7a1d","tid":2496673,"uid":175258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:41:45.000Z","msg":"錯而能改<br />\n<br />\n我收到破壞我荃辦犯錯青年的道歉信，我接受了他的道歉並原諒了他。<br />\n<br />\n機會是給予真誠認錯的人的。<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWUXvr7HLW3Pm181pjSDsEZJoZ7Aq1gBHTgZPeBEVD3Di?filename=DkJZ994.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDkJZ994.png&h=cebaf91c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f8447fb0fa336f07cd05b5f251b21936b010aa0","tid":2496673,"uid":175258,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:42:20.000Z","msg":"而家肯寫道歉信嘅年輕人好少應該俾機會佢．希望佢真係識得覺醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c631bec1e9f2d22ac4de2b3f4f1d0c4a6dbe1596","tid":2496673,"uid":175258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:42:45.000Z","msg":"少年人，真誠知錯，真誠悔改，機會總可令懺悔者從新起步！緊記銘記於心，莫再令任何人失望！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34bcb6c627c3587ea05ceea1e71657a8202d4177","tid":2496673,"uid":175258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:42:56.000Z","msg":"手足<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}